@startuml
actor User

participant PmsLoadSimulation
participant SimulationConfig
participant PmsEndToEndScenario
participant DoctorChains
participant PatientChains
participant AppointmentChains

participant "Doctor Service" as DoctorSvc
participant "Patient Service" as PatientSvc
participant "Appointment Service" as AppointmentSvc
participant "Gatling Engine" as Gatling

User -> PmsLoadSimulation : Run load test (mvn gatling:test)

PmsLoadSimulation -> SimulationConfig : Load configuration
SimulationConfig --> PmsLoadSimulation : URLs, users, duration

PmsLoadSimulation -> PmsEndToEndScenario : build()
PmsEndToEndScenario --> PmsLoadSimulation : ScenarioBuilder

PmsLoadSimulation -> Gatling : setUp() & injectClosed(users)

Gatling -> PmsEndToEndScenario : Execute scenario

PmsEndToEndScenario -> DoctorChains : createDoctor()
DoctorChains -> DoctorSvc : POST /v1/doctors
DoctorSvc --> DoctorChains : doctorId

PmsEndToEndScenario -> DoctorChains : getDoctorById()
DoctorChains -> DoctorSvc : GET /v1/doctors/{id}

PmsEndToEndScenario -> DoctorChains : getAllDoctors()
DoctorChains -> DoctorSvc : GET /v1/doctors

PmsEndToEndScenario -> PatientChains : createPatient()
PatientChains -> PatientSvc : POST /v1/patients
PatientSvc --> PatientChains : patientId

PmsEndToEndScenario -> PatientChains : getPatientById()
PatientChains -> PatientSvc : GET /v1/patients/{id}

PmsEndToEndScenario -> PatientChains : getAllPatients()
PatientChains -> PatientSvc : GET /v1/patients

PmsEndToEndScenario -> AppointmentChains : createAppointment()
AppointmentChains -> AppointmentChains : Build payload\n(doctorId, patientId)
AppointmentChains -> AppointmentSvc : POST /v1/appointments
AppointmentSvc --> AppointmentChains : appointmentId

PmsEndToEndScenario -> AppointmentChains : getAppointmentById()
AppointmentChains -> AppointmentSvc : GET /v1/appointments/{id}

Gatling -> Gatling : Collect metrics
Gatling -> Gatling : Generate HTML report

Gatling --> User : Gatling HTML report
@enduml
